title: Battle Fantasia -Revised Edition-
notes:
Performance itself is perfect. 

The button mapping options in the configuration options do not work regardless of controller. When double-clicking a button, it puts it as "Button 10" no matter what, instead of giving the option to change it.

In game videos do not work, and when a video is selected in the gallery it crashes the game. The videos are .wmv files.
specs: Intel i3-3250 (4) @ 3.500GHz / NVIDIA GeForce GTX 550 Ti

notes: Runs at hyperspeed in fullscreen mode, but is perfect in windowed mode, including controller support.
title: Battle Fantasia -Revised Edition-
